# Local development files that should not be copied into the image
# (but we are copying the whole source, so we don't need to ignore much)
# However, we might want to ignore the backups.json if it's large and not needed in the image? 
# But the application might need it for persistence. We'll not ignore it.

# Ignore the .git directory
